title: Is It Time to Panic About the Ravens, Packers, and Bills?
description:
Nora and Mal dive into the Baltimore Ravens and discuss their important matchup against the Kansas City Chiefs. They provide an assessment of their level of panic about the Ravens and four other teams that struggled in Week 1. They wrap up by answering a few listener questions.

Hosts: Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
